{"tid":896432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者戴口罩稱「空氣達標」 　遭當場質問","createTime":"2018-11-10T04:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T06:32:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc05a322581ccf5443cdc40f482dd6391d03a55","tid":896432,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181110/20542645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181110%2F20542645&d=gKsu5e2IlVg3nxeHSNKNbzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4bab3352\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181110%2F20542645&h=76650ae5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181110/20542645</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月10日 <br />\n<br />\n記者戴口罩稱「空氣達標」 　遭當場質問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181110/large/a1503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181110%2Flarge%2Fa1503a.gif&h=c71432cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「碳九」洩漏造成泉州泉港生態災難，出事後地方當局多次發通報稱「油污已全部清除完」，但被現場採訪的內媒記者揭發並非事實，指至昨日油污尚未沒清完、空氣仍刺鼻，認為官方只想粉飾太平。央媒譴責地方政府掩耳盜鈴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瀰漫濃烈柴油味<br />\n<br />\n前日當地環保廳宣稱「海面油污已基本清理完畢」，新華社記者事後到場見到，政府人員仍在海面放置吸油氈，清理污染物，顯示清理未結束。央視發評論文章指，官方多次稱「油污已全部清除完」，但前線調查揭發，支撐魚排的發泡膠被腐蝕，洩漏海面油污未打撈乾淨，多名村民不適入院。央視評論認為，洩漏看是意外，實則不簡單，「事故後沒聽到當局拉響空氣質量警報，沒看見組織漁民處理污染自救，倒是看到有人用高壓水槍在空氣質量監測點附近沖洗。凡此種種，都給人捂蓋子、掩耳盜鈴印象。」評論認為上級相關部門應盡早介入，對事件問責。<br />\n<br />\n泉港廣播電視台連日轉發官方通報，指泉港區空氣及水質達標，該台記者在場採訪時遭民眾斥責造假，「既然達標，你們為何還要戴着口罩（圖）採訪？」記者尷尬不己。有央媒記者走訪當地，距事發碼頭不足1公里的肖厝村仍嗅到瀰漫濃烈的類似柴油味，感到喉嚨難受、胸悶。<br />\n<br />\n央視  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n魚排老闆口麻痹入ICU　轟當局隱瞞<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n陝西地下水重金屬超標　羊群暴斃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魚排老闆口麻痹入ICU　轟當局隱瞞<br />\n陝西地下水重金屬超標　羊群暴斃<br />\n毒油污腐蝕眼珠福建現「生化魚屍」校方逼上課　多名小童不適"},{"pid":"9c604755bfe11ed78876d863ab18705c49743f4e","tid":896432,"uid":131522,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/123223_66caa5024f1dee6cd5f03deeed09783b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F123223_66caa5024f1dee6cd5f03deeed09783b.png&h=49e48a0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ee02f98e52c6816bcf77a83473f6a5f7c523d9f","tid":896432,"uid":37220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf5ec970ccdf40030bf25c32b5cc78d273b2b8f","tid":896432,"uid":59278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320f7b5a295b8b8e1501c854468d3863ced24027","tid":896432,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"認為官方只想粉飾太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一日先知咩支那人, 天津大爆炸後即刻噴綠油, 到依家都好似無下文咁, 中家都知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97e097fc02244a096749082a454f8c5ebdacbf1","tid":896432,"uid":64601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:02:01.000Z","msg":"個口罩黑撚過我條撚<img src=\"